kled inside as she saw Theseus's interest in the amazon.  Oh to be young and restless, she thought.  &quot;Well, if you shall both excuse me.  I think I need to go check on things with De'Lerium.&quot;  She nodded to them both and then gave a sly wink to Theseus.<br>
